      <title>在美元走强的情况下，中国通过削弱人民币汇率来放松对人民币的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/china-loosens-grip-on-yuan-by-weakening-fixing-as-dollar-gains</link>
